WITH 取得項目 AS( SELECT "T5"."serviceMeisho", "T5"."serviceKomokuCode", "T8"."serviceShuruiCode", "T8"."T1_sortYouKomokuCode" FROM rgdb."DbT7119ServiceCode" AS "T5" INNER JOIN ((SELECT "T2"."serviceTeikyoYM", "T2"."serviceShuruiCode" AS "T2_serviceShuruiCode", "T1"."sortYouKomokuCode" AS "T1_sortYouKomokuCode", "T2"."serviceKomokuCode" AS "T2_serviceKomokuCode" FROM "DbWT3470chohyouShutsuryokuyou" AS "T1" INNER JOIN "DbWT3470ToukeihyoMeisaichukan" AS "T2" ON "T1"."serviceShuruiCode" = "T2"."serviceShuruiCode" AND "T1"."sortYouKomokuCode" <= "T2"."serviceKomokuCode" GROUP BY "T2"."serviceShuruiCode", "T1"."sortYouKomokuCode", "T2"."serviceKomokuCode", "T2"."serviceTeikyoYM" ) AS "T7" INNER JOIN (SELECT MAX("T02"."serviceTeikyoYM") AS "T02_serviceTeikyoYM", "T02"."serviceShuruiCode", "T02"."serviceKomokuCode" AS "T02_serviceKomokuCode" FROM "DbWT3470chohyouShutsuryokuyou" AS "T01" INNER JOIN "DbWT3470ToukeihyoMeisaichukan" AS "T02" ON "T01"."serviceShuruiCode" = "T02"."serviceShuruiCode" AND "T01"."sortYouKomokuCode" <= "T02"."serviceKomokuCode" GROUP BY "T02"."serviceShuruiCode", "T02"."serviceKomokuCode", "T02"."serviceTeikyoYM" ) AS "T3" ON "T7"."T2_serviceShuruiCode" = "T3"."serviceShuruiCode" AND "T7"."T2_serviceKomokuCode" = "T3"."T02_serviceKomokuCode" AND "T7"."serviceTeikyoYM" = "T3"."T02_serviceTeikyoYM" ) AS "T8" ON "T5"."serviceShuruiCode" = "T8"."serviceShuruiCode" AND "T8"."T1_sortYouKomokuCode"<="T5"."serviceKomokuCode" AND "T5"."tekiyoKaishiYM" <= "T8"."serviceTeikyoYM" AND "T8"."serviceTeikyoYM" <= "T5"."tekiyoShuryoYM" )
SELECT "DbWT3470chohyouShutsuryokuyou".*, "T9"."serviceMeisho" FROM "DbWT3470chohyouShutsuryokuyou" INNER JOIN (SELECT "取得項目1"."serviceMeisho", "取得項目1"."serviceShuruiCode", "取得項目1"."T1_sortYouKomokuCode" FROM 取得項目 AS "取得項目1" INNER JOIN (SELECT "取得項目"."serviceMeisho", "取得項目"."serviceShuruiCode", MIN("取得項目"."serviceKomokuCode") AS "MIN_serviceKomokuCode" FROM "取得項目" GROUP BY "取得項目"."serviceMeisho", "取得項目"."serviceShuruiCode", "取得項目"."serviceKomokuCode" ) AS "取得項目2" ON "取得項目1"."serviceMeisho" = "取得項目2"."serviceMeisho" AND "取得項目1"."serviceShuruiCode" = "取得項目2"."serviceShuruiCode" AND "取得項目1"."serviceKomokuCode" = "取得項目2"."MIN_serviceKomokuCode" ) AS "T9" ON "DbWT3470chohyouShutsuryokuyou"."serviceShuruiCode" = "T9"."serviceShuruiCode" AND "DbWT3470chohyouShutsuryokuyou"."sortYouKomokuCode" = "T9"."T1_sortYouKomokuCode"
